# Menu

+++
--- demo ---
#### 菜单栏
用于导航
``` jsx
import { Menu, MenuItem } from 'zeus'

class MenuDemo extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <div style={{background: '#ccc', border: '1px solid #ccc'}}>
        <Menu
          value="1"
        >
          <MenuItem>
            menu 1
          </MenuItem>
          <MenuItem>
            menu 2
          </MenuItem>
          <MenuItem>
            menu 3
          </MenuItem>
        </Menu>
      </div>
    )
  }
}

```


